      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Why was my client disconnected from the cache?",
      "pos": [
        5261,
        5307
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The following are some common reason for a cache disconnect.",
      "pos": [
        5309,
        5369
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Client-side causes",
      "pos": [
        5375,
        5393
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The client application was redeployed.",
      "pos": [
        5402,
        5440
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The client application performed a scaling operation.",
      "pos": [
        5449,
        5502
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In the case of Cloud Services or Web Apps, this may be due to auto-scaling.",
      "pos": [
        5515,
        5590
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The networking layer on the client side changed.",
      "pos": [
        5599,
        5647
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Transient errors occurred in the client or in the network nodes between the client and the server.",
      "pos": [
        5656,
        5754
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The bandwidth threshold limits were reached.",
      "pos": [
        5763,
        5807
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "CPU bound operations took too long to complete.",
      "pos": [
        5816,
        5863
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Server-side causes",
      "pos": [
        5868,
        5886
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "On the standard cache offering, the Azure Redis Cache service initiated a fail-over from the primary node to the secondary node.",
      "pos": [
        5895,
        6023
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure was patching the instance where the cache was deployed",
      "pos": [
        6032,
        6092
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This can be for Redis server updates or general VM maintenance.",
      "pos": [
        6105,
        6168
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "What do the StackExchange.Redis configuration options do?",
      "pos": [
        6208,
        6265
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "StackExchange.Redis has many options.",
      "pos": [
        6267,
        6304
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This section talks about some of the common settings.",
      "pos": [
        6305,
        6358
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For more detailed information about StackExchange.Redis options, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>StackExchange.Redis configuration<ept id=\"p1\">](https://github.com/StackExchange/StackExchange.Redis/blob/master/Docs/Configuration.md)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        6359,
        6552
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "ConfigurationOptions",
      "pos": [
        6554,
        6574
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Description",
      "pos": [
